item.title: Markdown Cheatsheet
item.description: Hi there, this is my first post in blog. And I’d like to recap some markdown syntax in the first post. Headers # H1 ## H2 ### H3 #### H4 ##### H5 ###### H6 H1 H2 H3 H4 H5 H6 Emphasis *asterisks* or _underscores_ **asterisks** or __underscores__ **asterisks and _underscores_** ~~Scratch this.~~ asterisks or underscores asterisks or underscores asterisks and underscores Scratch this.
